OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cloudy this morning with
OL,6,Foutbreaks of rain, locally heavy in
OL,7,Fthe north at first, but becoming
OL,8,Flighter and more patchy. Brighter
OL,9,Fbreaks in the south during the
OL,10,Fafternoon, though further rain
OL,11,Farriving across the north later.
OL,12,FBreezy at first.
OL,13,
OL,14,CTonight:FRain clears away northwards
OL,15,Fthis evening, then turning much drier
OL,16,Fwith clearer spells overnight. Some
OL,17,Fmisty low cloud around coasts and in
OL,18,Fthe north. A very mild night to come.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
