OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FSome low cloud may affect
OL,6,FCumbria and areas near to the west
OL,7,Fcoast at times. Otherwise fine with
OL,8,Fsome very warm sunshine. Temperatures
OL,9,Fcontinue to rise above the May average.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FPatchy
OL,12,Frain Friday night. Very warm over the
OL,13,FBank Holiday weekend with plenty of
OL,14,Fsunshine and light winds. Any early
OL,15,Fmorning cloud burning back to the west
OL,16,Fcoast each day.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
